# $Id$

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is a lazy-k interpreter - basically a rewrite of lazy.cpp in PIR.
Lazy-k is a pure functional programming language following the SKI calculus

=head1 AUTHOR

leo

=head1 SEE ALSO

L<http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lazy_K_programming_language>

